name: Toss a coin
desc: This is a project where i made a coinflipper game. The player chooses heads or tails, and if the computer flips what they guess they get a point. This all gets synced to a sql database i host.

name: Shopheinz
desc: In this project we made a functioning webstore that used an API instead of PHP to interface with a database. Over the span of 3 months i went from not knowing any C# to being quite comfortable with the language.
